Class TreeModelUtils<T extends SequenceElement>

  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModelUtils<T>

    public class TreeModelUtils<T extends SequenceElement>
extends BasicModelUtils<T>
    This is VPTree-based implementation for wordsNearest method, suited for multiple consequent calls. Please note: VPTree will take some memory, dependant on your model size.
